Detailed Description

Obsolete. Does nothing. Don't use it.

" This abstract class simplifies the implementation of a basic two track effect where you want the values of both tracks together. Inherit from it if your effect doesn't just modifies a track in place and doesn't care how many samples it gets at a time. Your derived class only needs to implement GetEffectName, GetEffectAction, and ProcessSimplePairedTwoTrack. "
